0.1.name: wordpress/attachment-extender
0.1.description:
Give you the ability to upload files that you have in your Media Library.  It also let you insert more then one file into a post at a time.

Please submit any bugs or suggested improvements to https://github.com/bmsterling/Attachment-Extender/issues

Need this plugin customized or need a plugin created, contact me via my contact form at http://kenzomedia.com

Also available through twitter, @bmsterling
